title: 'Pop Up in the Rock' shows off renewed 9th Street
text:
'Pop Up in the Rock' shows off renewed 9th Street A quick pop-up festival took place on West 9th Street in Little Rock Saturday. LITTLE ROCK, Ark. (KTHV) - A quick pop-up festival took place on West 9th Street in Little Rock Saturday. 
Pop-up in the Rock stretched from ninth street and Broadway over to the corner of State and across to Philander Smith College, focusing on creating a new look for the area. 
Organizers now are trying to show the district's vitality and potential. The festival featured music, food and tours along with performances that were designed to encourage a sense of community.
